30:{"question":"What conditions does Dr Arjun specialise in?","answer":"Dr Arjun specialises in migraine, epilepsy, stroke rehabilitation, Parkinson's disease, and peripheral neuropathy. Both medical and procedural treatments are offered."}
31:{"question":"Is online consultation available?","answer":"Yes, teleconsultation is available via WhatsApp or phone call. Please contact the clinic to schedule an online consultation."}
32:{"question":"Can I get a second opinion?","answer":"Absolutely. Second opinion consultations are welcome. Please bring all previous reports, scans, and prescriptions for a thorough evaluation."}
33:{"question":"Which languages does Dr Arjun consult in?","answer":"Dr Arjun consults in English, Hindi, and Telugu to ensure clear communication with all patients."}
34:{"question":"Does Dr Arjun operate at multiple hospitals?","answer":"Yes, Dr Arjun is the lead consultant at Dr Arjun Neuro Care, Kondapur, and a visiting consultant at Yashoda Hospitals, Hyderabad."}
